     IINFDS       DS
     I                                    B 378 3790$$RRN
      *
      *(FCETL03).. PROCESS NAME M/F ...
     I* DELETE DUE DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A6GSHZ
     I                                        1   40A6GSYY
     I                                        5   60A6GSMM
     I                                        7   80A6SSDD
      *
      *(FCEPL01).. PART INFORMATION M/F ...
     I* DELETE DUE DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2GSHZ
     I                                        1   40A2GSYY
     I                                        5   60A2GSMM
     I                                        7   80A2GSDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@SYSTM
     I                                        7  140@SYSHZ
      * PART NO.
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 D2HIN
     I                                        1   5 D2HIN1
     I                                        6   6 D2HF1
     I                                        7  11 D2HIN2
     I                                       12  12 D2HF2
     I                                       13  14 D2HIN3
      *     <<
